data.description: Must see home with high ceilings, large rooms, three bedrooms, two full baths and a possible fourth bedroom on main floor! Close to Baden Walmart and walking distance to northern lights shopping center. Additional split unit was installed upstairs for more comfortable temperatures in summertime. This home has a very clean basement that walks out to integral garage with large fenced in backyard with an extra lot. Also, a side exit to the patio, and a rear exit to the covered back porch. Lots of parking it can fit up to four vehicles on property and has on street parking.
